<P>DISCOURSES on Various <HI>Important Subjects,</HI></P>
<P>Nearly concerning the great Affair of the Soul's Eternal Salvation, Viz.</P>
<LIST>
<ITEM>I. Ju&s;tification by Faith alone.</ITEM>
<ITEM>II. Pre&s;&s;ing into the Kingdom of GOD.</ITEM>
<ITEM>III. <HI>Ruth's</HI> Re&s;olution.</ITEM>
<ITEM>IV. The Ju&s;tice of GOD in the Damnation of Sinners.</ITEM>
<ITEM>V. The Excellency of JESUS CHRIST.</ITEM>
</LIST>
<P>Delivered at <HI>Northampton,</HI> chiefly at the Time of the late wonderful pouring out of the Spirit of GOD there.</P>
<P>By <HI>Jonathan Edwards,</HI> A. M.</P>
<P>Pa&s;tor of the Church of CHRIST in <HI>Northampton.</HI></P>
<Q><BIBL>Deut. iv. 8.</BIBL>
